The PIC16F877A acts as the main control unit of the system. It reads inputs from sensors and switches, processes the data according to the programmed logic, and controls outputs such as displays, relays, LEDs, or communication modules. All system operations are coordinated by this microcontroller.
2. 100 nF Decoupling Capacitor (Between VCC and GND)
