The 100 nF capacitor acts as a decoupling or bypass capacitor. It filters high-frequency noise and voltage spikes present on the power supply lines. During sudden switching inside the microcontroller, it provides instantaneous current and helps maintain a stable 5 V supply. This improves the reliability of the PIC16F877A.




3. 16 MHz Crystal Oscillator
